summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Alley in Block Thirty-nine (39) Capitol Hill Add. Division \#6 in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 21181, creating Local Improvement District No. 2087 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
